snippet.title: VGA 2011: Rainbow Six: Patriots Exclusive Trailer
snippet.description: Rainbow operatives are back in action against a threat unlike any they've faced before!  Get your intel on the Patriots in this Trailer from the Spike Video Game Awards of 2011!
